      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is very important that you **do not** combine St. John's Wort with sertraline without consulting your doctor first. These substances can interact with each other and potentially cause serious side effects, including serotonin syndrome. Please schedule an appointment with your prescribing physician or a pharmacist to discuss your increased anxiety and mood swings before making any changes to your medication regimen. They can safely advise you on appropriate next steps for managing your stress and mood.",
