      "content": "i get that, but i already talked to my pharmacist once and they just said it's a \"possibility\" but not common. i'm not looking to change my prescription, just wanted to add something natural to help through these next two weeks of exams. since st johns wort is just a plant, it shouldn't be as intense as the meds, right? like, can i just take a low dose so it stays safe?",
